{"tid":1649614,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"為幾個靈堂慶生撚樣就割蓆？","createTime":"2019-10-12T17:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T19:55:39.000Z","uid":181719,"like":407,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":122,"replies":[{"pid":"fb581133934a85f4d4e5ab06f5bbcbe64d0a0b5f","tid":1649614,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:32:54.000Z","msg":"首先利申，完全唔撚識班人，亦都覺得佢地應該公開道歉或者表演食屎裸跑 whatever.<br />\n<br />\n只係要問一句<br />\n<br />\n係咪咁就割蓆？<br />\n<br />\n咪撚再講果啲咩「批評唔等於割蓆」「唔割唔等於唔反省」啦屌，廢話黎<br />\n<br />\n包括我呢個post在內，一失咗焦就係失咗焦。<br />\n<br />\n最後再問一個問題：<br />\n<br />\n對家殺人都唔知殺咗幾多個啦，搵幾個人黎做場大龍鳳有幾撚難呀？"},{"pid":"798c0400170705c42379b2faf5bc893d23b53838","tid":1649614,"uid":181719,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:33:31.000Z","msg":"依家就散架喇，大家幫推啦"},{"pid":"f15ac08601763ccedc8f75f07f84aff0de729467","tid":1649614,"uid":181719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:33:43.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"b4a5744af79fdd3eabf96185b98c4ce68e6db0b0","tid":1649614,"uid":181719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:33:56.000Z","msg":"自推兩下"},{"pid":"cf1f1d679985ec9ee73a2d9197c91588d2663747","tid":1649614,"uid":181719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:34:09.000Z","msg":"無三不成幾"},{"pid":"f2d27a81a1934b01a9a5e8ff3fbb8e0531d7da98","tid":1649614,"uid":181719,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:34:25.000Z","msg":"老豆搵仔都停啦"},{"pid":"70b91a2261c5ab2323ea00eeda1ebd798a29653b","tid":1649614,"uid":242537,"like":21,"dislike":5,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:34:36.000Z","msg":"你會唔會去紅磡市立殯儀館度食蛋糕？"},{"pid":"7f92aa996a3651f4ab80b2d0b3decb940e91193d","tid":1649614,"uid":181719,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:34:54.000Z","msg":"民主派沒有分裂的本錢"},{"pid":"1802a331e705c3c6cde24c6f8f2368b9d5bab12b","tid":1649614,"uid":181719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019