動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193e1506951983e19d6a898b0a025784f8fbf865","tid":1649614,"uid":200216,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:45:00.000Z","msg":"點割？係到慶生係同路人？<br />\n一係就死出黎道歉先"},{"pid":"fe7947f4b52a523b55cfd0611dc0a65b1caab469","tid":1649614,"uid":298289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:46:02.000Z","msg":"嬲還嬲，因為2條友就停會唔會太意氣用事啊，對家知原來咁易搞分化，呢d事陸續有黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw佢地應該道歉"},{"pid":"d4f3cc95c26f77d18101b004bca694f353581b9f","tid":1649614,"uid":49847,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:46:35.000Z","msg":"岩 唔應該為左幾件On9而停晒<br />\n老豆又停國難又停 <br />\n打緊仗呀大佬<br />\nOn9同7仔一樣多 教訓唔晒架<br />\n唔好晒時間係佢地身上啦 屌幾句咪算囉"},{"pid":"8a72766af6604e20b2df5a129aae8aa6a1b62db2","tid":1649614,"uid":70852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:46:53.000Z","msg":"幾百萬人中既幾個傻鳩 小數黎"},{"pid":"9082e7666ac08e8de8edf6a84831f900c3b0b0ec","tid":1649614,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:47:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"315154e0faa77980dcf500709acdfc5cf5bec011","tid":1649614,"uid":181719,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:48:02.000Z","msg":"我唔再推喇，本身我開呢個po都係令件事失緊焦。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家記得乜野係核爆都唔割，乜野係正經事。<br />\n<br />\n如果「核爆都唔割」原來係有幾百萬樣前設嘅，咁其實呢句口號只係鳩噏架咋。<br />\n<br />\n大家繼續努力。<br />\n<br />\n最後，無論你班蛋糕撚係演員定真心膠。<br />\n<br />\n盡快道歉或者盡快死全家啦，唔該"},{"pid":"cf45d394611675c6e0976352fbf14d5dd9d083fd","tid":1649614,"uid":76960,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c015d880cd368a9f6d504cc6cac2534ec31780eb","tid":1649614,"uid":810,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:44:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vmp28Xu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvmp28Xu.jpg&h=0c9e3b74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n叫佢地解釋下 <br />